      • isCubeInIntake

        public static boolean isCubeInIntake()
        The method checks if the ultra sonic sensor is within a certain range. If the cube is within an inch of the sensor, then it will read any where from 0 to .28. If the cube is within 0 or .28, then it will read true. The cube is in the intake. If the cube is greater than .28, or less than 0, it will return false. The cube is not in the intake.
        Returns:
        if the cube is in the intake.
